Characters and Special Forces (Personnel) are most valuable to the Empire.  Personnel can engage in missions such as Espionage, Sabotage, and Recruitment. Characters are also capable of taking on leadership roles including 'Admiral', 'Commander', or 'General'. Special forces available to you include Imperial Commandos, Imperial Espionage Droids, Imperial Probe Droids, and Noghri Death Commandos. Our personnel should be used whenever possible to defeat the Rebel scum.